{
  "stem": "10272.7",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And he destroyed-- he opened the-- they had, in this-- in this-- in the basement, he had drums of oil and of-- and of gasoline, I mean, this petrol.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And all kinds of things which he had, he destroyed.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And he break everything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And he-- everything, he destroyed almost everything.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And he was getting hit with this-- the policeman was shooting at him.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "But he didn't kill him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So finally, he got calmed down.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he went to this-- to this-- he piped up.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my mother cried.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the kids were crying, asking him, Dad, don't do this.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Let's go.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So they went.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My brother, Charlie, was carrying on his back, the luggage.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he was very strong.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And all the-- two, two pieces of luggage he was carrying, one on the back, one in his hand.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they get to the train station over there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they were together in the same train with my father.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And Zelinger's there-- told my father, come and let's, let's get away.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Let's-- we, we can-- you can save your life.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he says, no, I'm not going to leave my wife with, with two kids.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Either we die all together, or we, we go-- we, we, we escape all together.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "This Zelinger, he, he went with this train.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they reached the border of Czechoslovakia and Poland on a town-- this is the, the last stop of the train-- Jasina, they call it.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "In Jasina, they get off the train.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they loaded them on a truck, on trucks.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And this truck take them-- took them to certain villages over there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And he-- in this village, he, Zelinger, escaped.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He ran away, left his wife there and his daughter.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And he escaped in the woods.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And he-- by-- on foot, he, he managed to get back to Budapest.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And in Budapest, I met him-- not in Israel.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I'm sorry.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I'm met him in Budapest.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And he told me this story in Budapest-- what happened.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And he says, that was the last time I saw your father and your mother together.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "They went.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "They took them from this village to Kamenets-Podolskiy.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "What happened on the way to Kamenets-Podolskiy, he doesn't know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "But there were other stories, which I heard from people from when I sold him these food stamps.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "They managed to survive in-- some of them survived from the-- from the pit from where they were killed.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So from them, I heard stories what happened, how they had to cross this river, [NON-ENGLISH], and-- on, on a-- on a bridge.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they are shooting on them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they jumped into the water.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they-- and they drowned in the water.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Some of them managed to, to swim across or swim away, and then to escape from this water.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "OK, we're going to pause now.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
